@@TJvSpecialImage.FadeIn
Description:
Use this method to fade in the image. The brightness property will go from 0 to 100. For a better result, don't use image bigger than 320*240, cause it could flicker.

================================================================
@@TJvSpecialImage.FadeOut
Description:
Use this method to fade out the image. The brightness property will go from 100 to 0. For a better result, don't use image bigger than 320*240, cause it could flicker.

