@@TJvSpecialImage.Brightness
Description:
Use this property to change the brightness of the image (from 0 to 200). 100 means no change, 0 means all colors to minimum and 200 means all colors to maximum.

================================================================
@@TJvSpecialImage.Flipped
Description:
Use this property to flip the image vertically. The first line will become the last one, etc...

================================================================
@@TJvSpecialImage.Inverted
Description:
Use this property to invert the image (All colors are inverted).

================================================================
@@TJvSpecialImage.Mirrored
Description:
Use this property to flip the image horizontally. For each line, the first pixel will become the last one, etc...

